    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented in collector-grade condition, this E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L V8, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The naturally aspirated power plant benefits from eight individual throttle bodies, providing an instantaneous throttle response and a linear power band that peaks at an 8,400 RPM redline. Mechanically, this vehicle is impeccable, with documented preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The chassis dynamics are preserved by a factory-calibrated suspension and a functional M-variable differential lock. The exterior retains its original depth and luster, free of any swirl marks or imperfections, while the interior leather maintains its factory matte finish with no bolster wear. This is a pristine example of the last atmospheric M-car, offering unrivaled mechanical purity.",
